"title": "5781: affection",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5781: affection",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Positive feelings towards another, often expressed in terms of attachment and warmth.</p>\n<h2>People and things arouse affection</h2>\n<h3>Whole churches</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:7\">PHP 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:13-2Cor7:15\">2CO 7:13–7:15</a></p>\n<h3>Friends</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:1\">1SA 18:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:3\">1SA 18:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:41-1Sam20:42\">1SA 20:41–20:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:36\">JHN 11:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:5\">ROM 16:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:9\">ROM 16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:12\">ROM 16:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:14\">COL 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:1\">3JN 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>Strangers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:13\">LUK 7:13</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The temple</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek24:21\">EZK 24:21</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Jerusalem</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:3-Neh1:4\">NEH 1:3–1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps137:6\">PSA 137:6</a></p>\n<h2>Affection is sometimes expressed in familial terms</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:16\">1SA 3:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:17\">1CO 4:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:16\">1SA 4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:11\">1SA 24:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:22\">2SA 18:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:12\">2KI 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:33\">JHN 13:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:13\">2CO 6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:1\">2TI 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:10\">PHM 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:13\">1PE 5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:28\">1JN 2:28</a></p>\n<h2>Emotions expressing affection</h2>\n<h3>Tenderness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:3\">GEN 34:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:38\">LUK 7:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1\">PHP 2:1</a></p>\n<h3>Longing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:8\">PHP 1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:1\">2SA 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:37\">MAT 23:37</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:34\">LUK 13:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:23\">ROM 15:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:11\">2CO 7:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:20\">GAL 4:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:26\">PHP 2:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:1\">PHP 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:4\">2TI 1:4</a></p>\n<h3>Openness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:11\">2CO 6:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:12-2Cor6:13\">2CO 6:12–6:13</a></p>\n<h3>Compassion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:36\">MAT 9:36</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:34\">MRK 6:34</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:26\">1KI 3:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:15\">ISA 49:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:20\">LUK 15:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:32\">EPH 4:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12\">COL 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:8\">1PE 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>Sorrow</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:4\">2CO 2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:14\">PSA 35:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:11\">LAM 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:2-Rom9:3\">ROM 9:2–9:3</a></p>\n<h3>Joy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:7\">PHM 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:15\">PRO 23:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:11\">PRO 27:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:14-Gal4:15\">GAL 4:14–4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:12\">2JN 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>Concern</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:14\">1CO 4:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:8\">PRO 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:6\">PRO 27:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:2-Prov31:3\">PRO 31:2–31:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:12\">ECC 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:7\">2CO 7:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:16\">2CO 8:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:19\">2CO 12:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:11-Gal4:12\">GAL 4:11–4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:19\">GAL 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:10\">PHP 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:18\">1TI 1:18</a></p>",
